      <!-- 1 -->
      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> No dedicated service pages</h4>
        <p>Your services are buried in a single page. Competitors have individual, optimized pages for each service -- and they rank for all of them. Combined, these keywords represent <strong>6,960 searches/month</strong>.</p>
        <div class="volume-tags">
