        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> No location-specific pages</h4>
        <p>Competitors have landing pages targeting surrounding towns -- Elkins Park, Jenkintown, Cheltenham, Montgomery County -- picking up local searches that Nexvel doesn't appear for at all.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3 -->
      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> Blog inactive since April 2020</h4>
        <p>Six posts in ten years. Meanwhile, competitors publish weekly, building keyword authority and driving consistent organic traffic. An active blog is the single biggest driver of long-tail search traffic.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 4 -->
      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> No industry-specific content</h4>
        <p>Nexvel has case studies in HVAC, dental, and legal verticals -- but no pages targeting the keywords people actually search. Those keywords have significant volume and low competition.</p>
        <div class="volume-tags">
