          <span class="volume-tag">"dental marketing" <span class="vol">2,400/mo</span></span>
          <span class="volume-tag">"HVAC marketing" <span class="vol">880/mo</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 5 -->
      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> Not visible on Google Maps</h4>
        <p>Nexvel does not appear in the top 10 results for "digital marketing agency Elkins Park PA." For "IT support Elkins Park PA," you show up at position 51 -- effectively invisible. Google Maps is where local buyers go first.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 6 -->
      <div class="check-item">
        <h4><span class="x-icon">X</span> Minimal social proof</h4>
        <p>Only <strong>7 Google reviews</strong> (4.9 stars) compared to <a href="https://needmomentum.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;">Momentum Digital</a>'s <strong>155 reviews</strong>. Instagram has 69 followers, Facebook has 102 likes. Review count and social presence factor into both search rankings and buyer trust.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
